<plot>Mark Wilson has been having nightmares of the masked murderer who killed his mother twelve years ago when he was a child. When Mark gets a call informing him that his father has been murdered he returns from college to his small hometown with a few friends for the funeral. Emotionally struggling with his life falling apart on him he is thrust into the mystery of trying to figure out who this masked murderer is and why they are killing off the people close to him. But will Mark figure it all out in time to save his friends or will it be too late?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188273</url></doc>
